
synchronizes a user's "pubd" account between multiple workstations

shpub provides tool for registering and settings options

base account is tied to machine
user can transition to shared account with register via user/pass 

scans ~/pub/ in order to synchronize new file content between shfs pubd:/pub/<user>/

marks shfs pubd:/pub/<user> as private owernship to user account.
allows pubd:/pub/<user>/<group> with shared group key.

